{
  "stem": "6989.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Which we happen to have had-- my father was a carpenter, so they built behind a closet what they call [NON-ENGLISH], which was like a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A bunker, exactly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And many a times we would go into that bunker when these things happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't seem to go into houses at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, like, they would just storm into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And sometimes I think maybe it's true, maybe not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I swear to you that at one time, I saw a German take a young kid.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had barrels, you know, for rain water, filled up full of rainwater.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He just dropped the kid in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that I saw with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we just ran into the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And once it was over, they had enough of blood sucking, sort of to speak, they left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they were not, like, constantly in the ghetto, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just knew that they were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, I just--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was quite something, as I remember it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember they had some kind of pills, like to dilute urine to water if necessary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course they put potatoes in and all kinds of dried goods, dried bread, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember it being very narrow as we walked in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to crouch to walk in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then it sort of opened up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they had, like, beds, like you would have bunk, bunk beds now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, they weren't exactly bunk beds, but narrow ones like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say maybe like my kitchen, 10 by 10, something, maybe 8 by 8.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, let's say, 4.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess about 8 or 10 people, not more. 8.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that area, I think it was standing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
